gengetopt: gengetopt (a tool to write command line option parsing code)
gengetopt:
gengetopt: Gengetopt is a tool to generate C code to parse the command line
gengetopt: arguments argc and argv that are part of every C or C++ program.
gengetopt: The generated code uses the C library function getopt_long to perform
gengetopt: the actual command line parsing. 
gengetopt: 
gengetopt: https://www.gnu.org/software/gengetopt/
